
Syntax i = 'i' (p) Where p Isa entity Else "Entities, please..."
Syntax b = 'b' (p) Where p Isa entity Else "Entities, please..."
Syntax s = 's' (p) Where p Isa entity Else "Entities, please..."

Add To Every entity
  Has i 3.
  Is b.
  Has s "string".

  Verb i Does Say i Of p. End Verb.
  Verb b Does If b Of p Then "b" End If. End Verb.
  Verb s Does Say s Of p. End Verb.
End Add.

The l Isa location
End The l.

The chair Isa object At l
End The chair.

Start at l.
  Increase i Of chair.

